753
01:00:09,936 --> 01:00:14,136
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ya. Aku yakin pelaku sebenarnya
berusia 30-an.</i></font>

754
01:00:14,336 --> 01:00:16,776
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini dengan 112 Emergency Call Center.
Ada yang bisa dibantu?</i></font>

755
01:00:17,266 --> 01:00:18,406
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Halo?</i></font>

756
01:00:18,406 --> 01:00:21,036
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Katakan. "Tolong aku."</i></font>

757
01:00:21,266 --> 01:00:23,066
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tolong.../
Apa?</i></font>

758
01:00:23,066 --> 01:00:24,066
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tolong...</i></font>

759
01:00:25,036 --> 01:00:27,666
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia ingin main-main dengan kita.</i></font>

760
01:00:27,666 --> 01:00:31,306
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia orang yang
