761
01:00:33,006 --> 01:00:34,006
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa ini?</i></font>

762
01:00:34,106 --> 01:00:36,736
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku yakin dia pelaku sesungguhnya
